FBIS3-38702 "drweu025_p_94002" FBIS-WEU-94-025 Document Type:Daily Report 7 Feb 1994 GREECE KKE Cautions Against Air Operation in Bosnia NC0602192894 Athens Elliniki Radhiofonia Radio Network in Greek 1800 GMT 6 Feb 94 NC0602192894 Athens Elliniki Radhiofonia Radio Network Language: Greek Article Type:BFN [Text] In a statement, the KKE [Greek Communist Party] has noted the danger of a general unrest in the Balkans because of the planned Western air attack in Bosnia-Herzegovina and has called on the government to block any NATO and CSCE decisions in this direction. The KKE has asked the country's political powers to clarify their position and condemn the manipulated intervention.
